rows.label: qev050905_MSG0002
rows.name:
If I may ask, are you the human BLADE who defeated
our prince, Ga Jiarg?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050905_MSG0003
rows.name:
...No. Forgive me. Past battles have no bearing on the
one we just fought. To use them as excuse is proof of
my own weakness.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050905_MSG0005
rows.name:
Though I do feel there was much to learn from the way
you fought, and I shall endeavor to do so.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050905_MSG0006
rows.name: I wish to keep these sensations fresh in my memory![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050905_MSG0007
rows.name: What say you to another match using Skells?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050905_MSG0008
rows.name:
I would like to try taking what I gleaned from the last
bout and applying it to Skell combat.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050905_MSG0009
rows.name:
That said, this is no place for large-scale combat.
We would first need to travel some ways out.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050905_MSG0010
rows.name: Will you favor me with another match?[ST:wait ]
